text: S - Do you plan your day? How?
P - Do you help your parents with grocery shopping? What do you do?
I - Do you make to-do lists? How often?
N - According to you, is your diet healthy or unhealthy? What does it include?
M - Does your family help you plan your weekend? How?
E - Have you ever done your own shopping? How would you spend 30 bucks on breakfast?
